{
  "title": "03 — Queue / Backlog",
  "uid": "kathir-03-queue",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "tags": [
    "kathir",
    "platform"
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 5
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 03 — Queue / Backlog\nThe segment→window→worker pipeline depth (Postgres `job_queue` via SKIP LOCKED, spec/10). Backlog = windows created but not yet processed by a worker; derived as `ingest_windows_created_total − model_clips_processed_total`. A persistently growing gap means workers can't keep up with ingestion. Metrics: `ingest_*`, `model_*`."
      },
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Windows created",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "blue"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(ingest_windows_created_total)",
          "legendFormat": "Windows created"
        }
      ],
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Clips processed (workers)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(model_clips_processed_total)",
          "legendFormat": "Clips processed (workers)"
        }
      ],
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Approx backlog",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "orange"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(ingest_windows_created_total) - sum(model_clips_processed_total)",
          "legendFormat": "Approx backlog"
        }
      ],
      "id": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Enqueue vs process rate /s",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "drawStyle": "line"
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(ingest_windows_created_total[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "enqueued"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(model_clips_processed_total[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "processed"
        }
      ],
      "id": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Approx backlog over time",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 17,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "marlin-metrics"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "drawStyle": "line"
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(ingest_windows_created_total) - sum(model_clips_processed_total)",
          "legendFormat": "backlog"
        }
      ],
      "id": 6
    }
  ]
}
